First, run in terminal:

export SPOTIPY_CLIENT_ID='ee31bafc26514072996d72e1b8387059'
export SPOTIPY_CLIENT_SECRET='5f561d59dcb14de7806bf2480cd7e8f6'

OR

export SPOTIPY_CLIENT_ID='5a84a4d59bb74cd8851f2c8796fd0d58'
export SPOTIPY_CLIENT_SECRET='bb792f367e314bfbad67f8fb1891a241'

Usage:
python Scraping.py [# Songs to write] [Artist ID] [Artist ID] [Artist ID]... 

# Search 5000 songs starting at Taylor Swift
python Scraping.py 5000 06HL4z0CvFAxyc27GXpf02

If the scraping terminates non-gracefully for any reason, you can run parsed_songs.py
to parse artists from the data folder rather than relying on seen_artists.txt